				<div class="entry-utility"><span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/category/dog-training-behavior" title="View all posts in Dog Training &amp; Behavior" rel="category tag">Dog Training &amp; Behavior</a></span> <span class="meta-sep meta-sep-tag-links">|</span><span class="tag-links"> Tagged <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/animal-cafe" rel="tag">Animal Cafe</a>, <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/command-vs-signal-in-dog-training" rel="tag">command vs signal in dog training</a>, <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/dr-roger-abrantes" rel="tag">Dr. Roger Abrantes</a>, <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/kelly-dunbar" rel="tag">Kelly Dunbar</a></span> <span class="meta-sep meta-sep-comments-link">|</span> <span class="comments-link"><a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/dog-training-behavior/master-commander-decoding-dog-training-terms#comments" title="Comment on Master &amp; Commander: Decoding Dog Training Terms">12 Comments</a></span></div><!-- .entry-utility -->
