				<div class="entry-utility"><span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/category/dog-training-behavior" title="View all posts in Dog Training &amp; Behavior" rel="category tag">Dog Training &amp; Behavior</a></span> <span class="meta-sep meta-sep-tag-links">|</span><span class="tag-links"> Tagged <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/k9-nose-work" rel="tag">K9 Nose Work</a>, <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/kelly-dunbar" rel="tag">Kelly Dunbar</a>, <a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/tag/national-association-of-canine-scent-work" rel="tag">National Association of Canine Scent Work</a></span> <span class="meta-sep meta-sep-comments-link">|</span> <span class="comments-link"><a href="http://willmydoghateme.com/dog-training-behavior/k9-nose-work-a-sport-even-frankie-can-love#comments" title="Comment on K9 Nose Work: A Sport Even Frankie Can Love">23 Comments</a></span></div><!-- .entry-utility -->
